A simple and interactive Counter App built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
This project helps beginners understand DOM manipulation, event handling, and basic JavaScript logic.

 Features:
1. Increase counter value
2. Decrease counter value
3. Reset counter
4. Real-time UI updates
5. Responsive design

Technologies Used:
1. HTML – Structure
2. CSS – Styling & layout
3. JavaScript – Logic & DOM manipulation
